  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "### Description\r\nWe currently use multiple RocksDB instances to split data across directories but could use `DBOptions.setDbPaths` to allow RocksDB to automatically spread data across multiple directories, including supporting target sizes for each directory.\r\n\r\nWe may still want to use separate hot and finalised DBs but allowing the finalised DB to be spread across multiple drives would be potentially useful.  Alternatively this may be a better options than having two DBs.",
